<https://semiceu.github.io/StatDCAT-AP_Copy/release/3.0.0#rdfs:ResourceShape/cd4869e0415166799e4cc19b3f0f6550cdfc1e9a> rdfs:seeAlso "https://semiceu.github.io/StatDCAT-AP_Copy/release/3.0.0#Resource.dimension";
